name: NewsstandDownloadAssetProps
summary: A dictionary of properties to pass to the method

properties.name: filename
properties.summary: The name of the file to be downloaded. If no name is specified here, the filename will be the last component of the url. (optional)

properties.name: url
properties.summary: Location of the asset to be downloaded

properties.name: userInfo
properties.summary: A dictionary of properties that can be passed through with the request to the event listeners. (optional)
properties.description: Warning: Do not include anything more than simple key value pairs. Including Titanium objects in userInfo will cause errors.
